items.title: Crisis 911
items.headline: Go Throught a Crisis Faster, Easier and With Less Struggle.
objectives_summary: It will teach you what you should and should not do right in the middle of the tough situation where you feel lost, things are falling apart, and you find that you don't have the energy. The moments when you specifically need to act correctly, taking efficient steps towards resolving the situation.   I will be speaking about your emergency self-services. These self-services are things you can do in order to prevent the situation from getting worse. And opposite to that - you will learn how to resolve the situation as fast and as easily as possible.  I will be teaching you simple techniques, exercises, methods which are based on the principles of self-management.  The principle of Self-management means - you don't need external help from anyone else to follow those methods and apply these techniques. No coach, teacher, or therapist. You can do this by yourself.
